      "commits": [
        {
          "message": "Reinstate LA LDH `report_pdf` field and disable PDF API (#1377)\n\nThis partially reverts fb1007d8, which allowed us to test the PDF API,\nbut has not been promoted into production by LA LDH yet. For the run\noccurring this Monday, we need to back out these changes.\n\nThis also makes the values configurable per-environment so testing\ncan continue in lower environments.",
          "url": "https://github.com/DSACMS/iv-cbv-payroll/commit/b5214f6673b57d374c82a2e9159539fba2dbccc1",
          "author": "Tom Dooner",
          "created_at": "2026-02-12T22:25:29+00:00"
        },
        {
          "message": "Sort changes in deploy notes (#1373)",
          "url": "https://github.com/DSACMS/iv-cbv-payroll/commit/19557480c25c95d467e6d45538ec5cbe7c6aa482",
          "author": "Ben Calegari",
          "created_at": "2026-02-12T21:09:05+00:00"
        },
        {
          "message": "FFS-3764: Update mileage deduction calculation for 2026 IRS rates (#1376)",
          "url": "https://github.com/DSACMS/iv-cbv-payroll/commit/45aa610523f00fe15b299fc8365acec73beedb33",
          "author": "Daphne Gold",
          "created_at": "2026-02-12T19:31:28+00:00"
        },
        {
          "message": "FFS-3758: Fix employer search button disabled after \"back\" (#1355)\n\nThis seems to be caused by the Turbo cache saving the frame with the\ndisabled button and our use of action=\"advance\" (meaning the user can\npress the Back button to get back to it).\n\nThe stimulus controller is reconnected every time, let's just re-enable\nthis button here. I tried to reproduce this on other buttons in the app,\nto no avail, so I think it's only this place that needs the fix.",
          "url": "https://github.com/DSACMS/iv-cbv-payroll/commit/0d96c8da8c2b53126ceceddfd10a363da921f5a5",
          "author": "Tom Dooner",
          "created_at": "2026-02-11T17:03:40+00:00"
        },
        {
          "message": "Bump axe-core-rspec from 4.11.0 to 4.11.1 in /app (#1366)\n\nCo-authored-by: dependabot[bot] <49699333+dependabot[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>",
          "url": "https://github.com/DSACMS/iv-cbv-payroll/commit/dbecd5ee63d126c69505f5d5b78a79eca252a0a9",
          "author": "dependabot[bot]",
          "created_at": "2026-02-11T14:00:47+00:00"
        },
        {
          "message": "Bump faraday from 2.14.0 to 2.14.1 in /app in the bundler group across 1 directory (#1369)\n\nCo-authored-by: dependabot[bot] <49699333+dependabot[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>",
          "url": "https://github.com/DSACMS/iv-cbv-payroll/commit/88d58149870fea99c75d52781c65f1c39ba7c824",
          "author": "dependabot[bot]",
          "created_at": "2026-02-11T14:00:25+00:00"
        },
        {
          "message": "FFS-3611: Never time out users on /synchronizations (#1356)\n\nThis works surprisingly well - by simply not rendering the timeout\nmodal, the synchronizations page can loop indefinitely. This will allow\nusers to remain on this page for >30 minutes, should they be so\ndetermined.\n\nI tested this locally by setting the timeout to 2 minutes (with a 1\nminute warning period) and then disabling Ngrok during the sync (to make\nit hang indefinitely). I was never timed out.",
          "url": "https://github.com/DSACMS/iv-cbv-payroll/commit/766dcca4a895589075e72c69257c524d2ecfe982",
          "author": "Tom Dooner",
          "created_at": "2026-02-11T01:46:11+00:00"
        },
        {
          "message": "FFS-3736: Activity Hub copy changes and activity cards (#1359)\n\n* Many content and UI updates on the Activity Hub\n* Cards are now used to represent completed activity flows (one per executed flow)",
          "url": "https://github.com/DSACMS/iv-cbv-payroll/commit/efbb8fb961a81c3ce6c16ea34fd9d0b34bd20595",
          "author": "Tim Miller",
          "created_at": "2026-02-10T23:31:34+00:00"
